name: Myn Kyneugh
Lore: 'Royal guard leader. Remembers nothing of his past other than serving his Emperor. Early instructor of Kir Kanos and Carnor Jax.',
Text: 'Deploys only on Coruscant or to Emperor''s site (or related site). When armed with a Force pike, adds one battle destiny. Your troopers and Royal Guards may ''react'' to here for free. Adds 1 to defense value of other Royal Guards at same and related sites.',
